HEADWORD: Slugger
<hw>Slug"ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who strikes heavy
blows; hence, a boxer; a prize fighter.</def> <mark>[Cant or
Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- (Baseball) A player with a high batting average, esp. one who
hits many home runs. -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slugging match</ent>⟦br⟧
